Happy Holidays!!! We just received the Best Christmas Gift!! Excited to Announce that "Place in the Sun" Pretty Poison-Jade Starling feat Lee Dagger  Tazmania Records @tazmaniarecords has officially hit #1 on the New Music Weekly Top 40 Indie Music Singles Chart, #7 on the Top 40 Radio Chart and #17 on the Hot 100 Chart!! Feeling So Blessed to have such an Amazing Promo Team, without them none of this would be possible ..A Heartfelt Special Thanks to @henryvargasmusic and @danmathews_klubjumpers @larry_peace_music @newmusicweeklymagazine for your Love, Support, Hard Work and Dedication to this record. We Love You So Much,You are The Best!! Thanks to all the Top 40 Radio stations ,Mixshows and Iheartradio for all the airplay!! Sending Love and Appreciation to all the DJs and Producers for your phenomenal mixes!! Klubjumpers, @sammichael_klubjumpers @lucadebanaireofficial
